# Example firewall policy (illustrative)

- Default deny on ingress
- Allow established and related connections
- Allow WireGuard UDP on the public interface
- Restrict administrative access to trusted infrastructure
- Allow Tor SOCKS access only from VPN subnets
- Block Tor SOCKS access from public interfaces
- Allow VPN forwarding only for explicitly permitted paths
- Enforce no clearnet egress for Tor-only VPN paths
